videos.description: Shakif Seymour scores from one yard out to give the Rockets a 17-3 lead in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Seymour plunges in for Toledo TD

videos.description: Logan Woodside finds Jordan Fisher for a 27-yard gain to put the Rockets in the red zone.
videos.headline: Fisher's 27-yard grab puts Toledo in the red zone

videos.description: Reece Goddard finds Tyron Arnett for a 26-yard touchdown pass to draw the Broncos closer 24-10.
videos.headline: Goddard to Arnett draws Western Michigan closer

videos.description: Logan Woodside connects with Diontae Johnson for a 13-yard touchdown to extend the lead for the Rockets in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Woodside and Johnson extends the margin for Toledo

videos.description: Toledo's Ka'dar Hollman intercepts Reece Goddard in the end zone for the Rockets in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Hollman's INT seals the deal for Toledo

videos.description: The Toledo Rockets clinch the MAC West with a dominating 37-10 victory over Western Michigan. Behind Logan Woodsides two touchdown pass performance.
videos.headline: Toledo to the MAC Championship Game
